description:
My place is close to Astoria Park, Hellgate on the Park, 7 minutes from Train Station (N,Q) and approximately 10-15 minutes into Manhattan. 

Laundry is located on the same block nearby. 

My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, business travelers, and families (with infants and young children).

Nearby from all trendy Astoria nightlife including restaurants and bars.
name: Cozy 1 Bedroom Trendy Astoria
review: The host canceled this reservation 35 days before arrival. This is an automated posting.
